        {
            "title": "ING:英鎊利率下降速度可能快於歐元區",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zunqbCIhoRRDomQwiXR_sA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC3L19Y_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 歐元/英鎊在週二因利率差距收窄而出現上行波動,但在週三上午歐洲央行利率預期下降後走低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">ING表示,兩個因素可能推動英國的鳩派重新定價幅度超過歐元區。英國央行在戰爭開始前就已準備好降息。英國也預計將在經合組織國家中面臨能源衝擊帶來的最大增長影響,這提供了鳩派論據。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國央行官員在最近的會議外評論中聽起來不那麼鷹派。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">ING維持對歐元/英鎊上行的傾向,預計整個英國央行的緊縮政策將被完全消化。該行認為0.880是該貨幣對的現實目標。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4d1c3ed3-1760-3d63-8d48-3c9f875fa6ba-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至格林威治標準時間上午10:55,英鎊兌美元走強,英鎊/美元報1.3310,上漲0.6%。歐元兌英鎊走弱,歐元/英鎊報0.8717,下跌0.2%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自2月28日中東戰爭爆發以來,英鎊一直波動劇烈,最新進展是美國總統唐納德·川普表示美軍將在兩到三週內撤離伊朗。川普稱他消除該國核威脅的目標已經實現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國央行金融政策委員會週三警告稱,中東衝突已對全球經濟造成重大衝擊,透過更高的能源價格和波動的市場增加了金融穩定風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以色列和美國與伊朗之間的衝突實際上已經停止了通過霍爾木茲海峽的航運,並減少了海灣地區的能源生產。油價飆升至每桶100美元以上,布蘭特原油達到衝突前水平的60%以上。歐洲和英國天然氣價格較衝突前水平上漲超過70%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/ing-%E8%8B%B1%E9%8E%8A%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%BF%AB%E6%96%BC%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83%E5%8D%80-120612447.html",
